# Akademiata WordPress theme

- **Repo:** https://github.com/irynaBilousSPDev/deAtaCennik.git (`origin`)
- **Optional remote:** `ata2026` Ôćĺ https://github.com/arinabilous/ata2026.git (only when user asks)
- **Text domain:** `akademiata` for all `__()`, `_e()`, `_x()`, `esc_html_e()`
- **Stack:** WordPress, ACF, WPML, Gulp (SCSS), Webpack (JS), Bootstrap 4 CDN (not npm BS5 on front)

## `functions.php` load order

`cpt-taxonomy.php` Ôćĺ `utilities.php` Ôćĺ `offer-pricing.php` Ôćĺ `ajax_filters.php` Ôćĺ `configure.php` Ôćĺ `js-css.php` Ôćĺ `shortcodes.php` Ôćĺ `breadcrumbs-functions.php` Ôćĺ `duplicate-cpt-posts.php` Ôćĺ `acf.php` Ôćĺ `load-cpt-slider.php` Ôćĺ `class-wp-mega-menu-walker.php` Ôćĺ `generate_keys_bch_mst.php` Ôćĺ `admin.php` (admin only). `wpml-string.php` is commented out.

## Build

```bash
npm install && npm run build   # or npm run dev
```

Edit `assets/src/` Ôćĺ outputs `assets/dist/css/main.css` and `assets/dist/js/{main,ajaxFilter,ajaxSlider,vendors}.js`. Rebuild after SCSS/JS changes.

## PHP conventions

- New helpers: prefer `akademiata_*` prefix; legacy `ata_*` for smart keys / news URLs.
- Match existing style in the file you edit (tabs vs spaces, `get_template_part` vs `locate_template`).
- **Windows:** never use PowerShell `Set-Content -Encoding UTF8` on theme PHP (breaks Polish characters).

## Cross-cutting behavior

- **Registration CTA:** show when `register_url` ACF is non-empty (`!empty($register_url)`).
- **Bachelor/master terms cache:** `akademiata_get_offer_terms()` in `utilities.php` ÔÇö for performance on offer singles/cards, not for PG/MBA detail blocks (use `get_the_terms()` there).
- **logical_sync_key:** auto-generated on bachelor/master save (`configure/generate_keys_bch_mst.php`); powers Google calculator on single offers.

## External data

- Prices JSON: Google Apps Script (`configure/js-css.php` Ôćĺ `googleApiUrl`), docs in `apps-script/README.md`, fallback `prices.json`.
- YouTube: `youtube-proxy.php` + `__YouTubeSlider.js`.

## Cursor rules

- Architecture docs: `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` ÔÇö update when code changes (`akademiata-maintain-rules.mdc`).
- Full audit: run **`/sync-rules`** after large refactors.
- Git: solo workflow on **`main`** ÔÇö **`/pr`** = commit (if needed) + push `origin main`; PR optional. Commit messages: **English only**. UI strings in PHP stay Polish (`akademiata` text domain). Say ÔÇťcommit onlyÔÇŁ or ÔÇťpush onlyÔÇŁ to limit `/pr` steps.
- **Dev deploy:** **`/deploy-dev`** = commit (if dirty) Ôćĺ push `origin main` (if ahead) Ôćĺ `npm run deploy:dev` (SFTP). Say **deploy only** / **without commit** to SFTP-upload only (skip git).
